2. cs.GR (Graphics) is also a likely category as the paper deals with correcting distortions caused by refractive surfaces such as glass.
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper uses deep learning techniques to correct image distortions.
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper uses a neural network to estimate and correct distortions.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with image processing and correction.
